---
source: crates/runtime/tests/models/search.rs
description: "SELECT question, answer, trunc(score, 3) as score FROM vector_search(qs, 'secondary') where id > 10 order by score desc, id LIMIT 4"
---
+---------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |
+---------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | Projection: vector_search(qs, Utf8("secondary")).question, vector_search(qs, Utf8("secondary")).answer, score                                                                                                             |
|               |   Sort: score DESC NULLS FIRST, vector_search(qs, Utf8("secondary")).id ASC NULLS LAST, fetch=4                                                                                                                           |
|               |     Projection: vector_search(qs, Utf8("secondary")).question, vector_search(qs, Utf8("secondary")).answer, trunc(vector_search(qs, Utf8("secondary")).score, Int64(3)) AS score, vector_search(qs, Utf8("secondary")).id |
|               |       TableScan: vector_search(qs, Utf8("secondary")) projection=[answer, id, question, score], full_filters=[vector_search(qs, Utf8("secondary")).id > Int64(10)]                                                        |
| physical_plan | ProjectionExec: expr=[question@0 as question, answer@1 as answer, score@2 as score]                                                                                                                                       |
|               |   SortPreservingMergeExec: [score@2 DESC, id@3 ASC NULLS LAST], fetch=4                                                                                                                                                   |
|               |     SortExec: TopK(fetch=4), expr=[score@2 DESC, id@3 ASC NULLS LAST], preserve_partitioning=[true]                                                                                                                       |
|               |       ProjectionExec: expr=[question@2 as question, answer@0 as answer, trunc(score@3, 3) as score, id@1 as id]                                                                                                           |
|               |         RepartitionExec: partitioning=RoundRobinBatch(3), input_partitions=1                                                                                                                                              |
|               |           ProjectionExec: expr=[answer@3 as answer, id@0 as id, question@1 as question, score@2 as score]                                                                                                                 |
|               |             HashJoinExec: mode=CollectLeft, join_type=Left, accumulator=MinMaxLeftAccumulator, on=[(id@0, id@1), (question@1, question@2)], projection=[id@0, question@1, score@2, answer@3]                              |
|               |               CoalescePartitionsExec                                                                                                                                                                                      |
|               |                 ProjectionExec: expr=[union_extract(json_get(key@0, id), int) as id, union_extract(json_get(key@0, question), str) as question, 1 - distance@1 as score]                                                  |
|               |                   FilterExec: union_extract(json_get(key@0, id), int) > 10                                                                                                                                                |
|               |                     CooperativeExec                                                                                                                                                                                       |
|               |                       RepartitionExec: partitioning=RoundRobinBatch(3), input_partitions=1                                                                                                                                |
|               |                         BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                                |
|               |                           CooperativeExec                                                                                                                                                                                 |
|               |                             S3VectorsQueryExec: limit=30                                                                                                                                                                  |
|               |               SchemaCastScanExec                                                                                                                                                                                          |
|               |                 BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                                        |
|               |                   DataSourceExec: partitions=1, partition_sizes=[1]                                                                                                                                                       |
|               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |
+---------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
